1.caption_en:
A blank "Platform Opportunity" canvas template for mapping a multi‑sided platform business: it organizes Consumers, Partners and Producers around a central Core Value Proposition and includes sections for market, revenue model, capabilities, data/intelligence, infrastructure and ecosystem impact.

